/*!
 * PLACEHOLDER — Toast UI Editor (3.x) UMD bundle NOT vendored.
 *
 * PLAN.md §3 asks for the real `toastui-editor-all.min.js` to be downloaded
 * once and committed here. In the environment this repo was built in,
 * outbound HTTPS to the Toast UI CDN (uicdn.toast.com) was blocked by
 * network policy, and the `@toast-ui/editor` npm package's own dist bundle
 * is not a standalone browser bundle (it `require()`s prosemirror-* and
 * other peer packages that a plain <script> tag cannot resolve), so it
 * could not be substituted either.
 *
 * This file intentionally defines no globals. app/static/js/editor.js
 * detects the absence of `window.toastui` and falls back to a plain
 * textarea + minimal toolbar editor (heading/bold/italic/strike/quote/
 * lists/link/highlight/image-upload), so the editor page remains fully
 * functional without this bundle.
 *
 * To enable the real WYSIWYG editor: replace this file with the genuine
 * `toastui-editor-all.min.js` from Toast UI Editor 3.x, and editor.js will
 * use it automatically — no other code changes needed.
 */
